OL,3,CBody found in search for teenager
OL,4,Cmissing after entering lake
OL,6,FA body has been found in the search
OL,7,Ffor a boy who got into trouble in a
OL,8,Flake in Lincoln.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FSwanholme Lakes at 2.30pm on Sunday
OL,12,Fafter reports that 15-year-old Declan
OL,13,FSawyer had entered the water and was
OL,14,Fmissing.
OL,16,FLincolnshire Police said in a
OL,17,Fstatement on Sunday evening: "We can
OL,18,Fupdate that our dive team have sadly
OL,19,Ffound a body in the water at Swanholme
OL,20,FLakes, Lincoln.
OL,26,@yD@^OU
