OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1779804667
OL,3,CBody found in search for teenager
OL,4,Cmissing after entering lake
OL,6,F"With agreement from the family we can
OL,7,Fshare that the boy who died is 15-year-
OL,8,Fold Declan Sawyer.
OL,10,F"Our thoughts are with his family and
OL,11,Fwe send our condolences at this
OL,12,Fincredibly difficult time.
OL,14,F"This is such a sad incident that will
OL,15,Fno doubt also affect many of Declan's
OL,16,Ffriends and the local community as
OL,17,Fwell."
OL,19,FOfficers had scoured the lakes for the
OL,20,Fboy with the help of their underwater
OL,21,Fsearch team.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUyD@FO]
