OL,3,CBody found in search for teenager
OL,4,Cmissing after entering lake
OL,6,F"As we are starting half-term week, we
OL,7,Fask our community to make sure that
OL,8,Fanyone affected is looked after and
OL,9,Fthat people are encouraged to seek
OL,10,Fhelp and support where they need it,"
OL,11,Fa force spokesperson said.
OL,13,FLincolnshire Police asked people not
OL,14,Fto speculate or share information that
OL,15,Fhad not come from an official source.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@eO]
